-- Louisville Beats Cincinnati 50-44 in Big East Championship Game
-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 2012-03-11T04:14:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-11/louisville-beats-cincinnati-50-44-in-big-east-championship-game.html
The University of Louisville
defeated the University of Cincinnati 50-44 in the Big East
Conference Championship game at Madison Square Garden in  New
York .  Louisville won the title for the second time since the
Cardinals joined the conference in the 2005-06 season. The first
championship victory was in 2009.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nancy Kercheval at 
 nkercheval@bloomberg.net  